night unto night is a 1949 film noir drama film directed by don siegel and written by kathryn scola . it is based on the 1944 novel by philip wylie . the film stars ronald reagan , viveca lindfors , broderick crawford , rosemary decamp , osa massen and art baker . the film was released by warner bros. on june 10 , 1949 . fifteen years later , siegel would direct reagan 's final film , 1964 's the killers .